item.title: CVE-2023-37490|2024-08-02T17:16:30.325Z -- sap_se -- sap%20businessobjects%20business%20intelligence%20%28installer%29
item.description: SAP Business Objects Installer - versions 420, 430, allows an authenticated attacker within the network to overwrite an executable file created in a temporary directory during the installation process. On replacing this executable with a malicious file, an attacker can completely compromise the confidentiality, integrity, and availability of the system
